Project Charter Template

Tagline:

Overview: 
- Describe in a paragraph the business opportunity met by this project (Why?)
- Describe in a paragraph the user value from this project (What?)
- Describe the success criteria for the project

Identify Constraints: (Resources, Dates)

Identify Stakeholders (internal)

Identify potential Users (external)

Agree on the project process. Normally:
  Develop a Vision
  Create a feature list (backlog)
  Size and Prioritize the backlog
  Set milestones based on dates or functionality
  Agree on the development process
  Agree on a release plan
  Identify test sites / users

Expose any Assumptions

Discover Risks

Agree on methods of Documentation
